---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="CSAE Policy | SkyThrow" lang="en" path="/en/csae/">
  <section class="text-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">CSAE Policy</p>
    <h1>Child Sexual Abuse and Exploitation Policy</h1>
    <div class="policy-card">
      <p>SkyThrow strictly prohibits child sexual abuse and exploitation and does not tolerate related content or activities.</p>
      <p>SkyThrow specializes in posting and does not store content. Content monitoring and enforcement are handled by the destination services, such as Bluesky.</p>
      <p>The project complies with applicable laws and international standards and works to support child protection.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
